| C-2 | **Detector refs stylistic inconsistency.** H030/H031 in `choir-doctrine.md` have `detector refs:` blocks but H001–H029 do not. This is correct per C3 scope; Phase B/E should backfill for other heresies as their detectors are created. | `docs/choir-doctrine.md:1145–1147, 1184–1186` | Only two heresy entries have detector refs. Consistent with scope but creates registry inconsistency. |

